        ],
        [
          "As a child you could see them.  The dead walked through the halls of your house and sat with you at school.. You said nothing of them, but you coudl hear them and sometimes you could see them.  When the vampires came for you and your family you were  not surprised.  The dead had told you they were coming and you thought you coudl finally be with them.  While you reveled in your vampiric existence, you alwasy felt dissapoointment that the secrets of true death still waited beyound the shroud in the Shadowlands.  You studied the path of Death and the Soul, but still the secrets of the soul elluded you.  Wraiths and spectres taught you many things, but always they keep the best secrets to themselves, especially the spectres who alwasy tempt you into danger with their tricks.  But it is so hard to say no when secrets are on the line.  Your pack depends on you to keep a safe haven and to find the places of power they need to satisfy the wizards of the Black Hand... but you have questions you need answered."
        ],
